formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
To the Best of my Knowledge, the data is true and fair. 
BCR Pending Bank Transactions details are provided for the RERA 70% Account with ICICI Bank as on 31-01-2022, Unsecured Loans are certified by Management. Booked Inventory include certain payments received in Bank Accounts other than the RERA Account. 
This has been disclosed by the management. however, the management certifies its end use for Cost of Construction. 
The date of Agreement to Sale are not verifiable from our end as the said details are not in the possession of the management.  Further, the certificate is prepared by placing reliance on the unaudited financial statements and books of account. Agreement to Sale are not verifiable as they are not available with the management. 
Further, an expenditure towards Land Development Premiums amounting to Rs. 1.62crores has been reclassified in order to present actual Cost of Project incurred and paid from the section Land cost to Construction Cost in this Certificate and now onwards.

Estimates of certain units have been changed as the promoter received more amount towards certain units namely B 802, D1403 D 1104 and D 1404.
Further, the local body has issued part BU Permissions in the case of Tower C and D and the same has been attached along with the Architect Certificate for your immediate reference.

The project stands completed as on the date of filing this report and QE shall also be filed immediately after the filing of the report.
